      "module_path": "track::composition_root",
      "docs": "Composition root for the track command family. Unit struct: no adapter dependencies are injected at construction time, each method wires its own adapters inline (in-method composition). Extended by this track with catalogue_lint_check_active_track(), which delegates to RunCatalogueLintInteractor to run the primitive-obsession catalogue lint gate across every tddd.enabled layer of the active track (ADR 2026-07-01-0004 D5: blocking from day one). All 39 of TrackCompositionRoot's inherent methods (38 pre-existing, spread across composition_root.rs / resolution.rs / ops.rs / fixpoint_resolve.rs / set_commit_hash.rs / mod.rs / tddd.rs under apps/cli-composition/src/track/, plus this track's 1 new method) are exhaustively declared below in inherent_impls, source-verified method-by-method against those 7 files (shim.rs / service_impl.rs, also declared as modules under track::, confirmed to contribute zero inherent TrackCompositionRoot methods). Exhaustive declaration -- not the partial, single-method declaration originally left here -- is required because action: modify's structural-equality evaluator (structs_structurally_equal in libs/infrastructure/src/tddd/signal_evaluator_v2/structural_eq.rs) performs an exact-match comparison against the type's full, merged inherent-method set; a partial declaration resolves to a non-blocking Yellow Mismatch signal that still blocks this track's own pre-review gate (bin/sotp task-contract check) for as long as the owning task remains done/in_progress, so partial declaration was not viable once Phase 4 implementation surfaced the mismatch. This exhaustive-declaration approach mirrors the pre-existing, currently-Blue precedent set by ReviewCompositionRoot (also a CompositionRoot-role unit struct, also action: modify) in track/items/pre-review-task-contract-conformance-gate-2026-06-27/cli_composition-types.json.",
      "spec_refs": [
        { "file": "track/items/catalogue-primitive-obsession-guard-2026-07-01/spec.json", "anchor": "IN-12" },
        { "file": "track/items/catalogue-primitive-obsession-guard-2026-07-01/spec.json", "anchor": "CN-07" }
      ],
      "informal_grounds": []
